            "id": 123823,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code une condition pour suggérer un restaurant si le <code>diet</code> de l'utilisateur est égal à <code>vegetarian</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"diet = \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"veggie_restaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Root&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"restaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;DelPosto&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" diet == \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Try out: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(veggie_restaurant)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"80\" endIndex=\"82\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"95\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Try out: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Root\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>==</code> suivi de <code>\"vegetarian\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
